/-- The matrix `T = [[1,1],[0,1]]` as an element of `SL(2,‚Ñ§)` -/
def T : SL(2,‚Ñ§) := ‚ü®![![1, 1], ![0, 1]], by norm_num [matrix.det_fin_two]‚ü©

/-- The matrix `T' (= T‚Åª¬π) = [[1,-1],[0,1]]` as an element of `SL(2,‚Ñ§)` -/
